data.name: lblHelp.Text
data.value: You are Red. When the progress bar on the left hand side is full, land on a home square to get the next goal. Completing the 5th goal wins the game. Read the game log on the right; it's useful. I didn't have enough time to make the 3 CPU players do anything, but they wouldn't be able to interfere with you winning anyway. I also didn't have enough time to make it so the same question is not repeated; sorry if that happens. Let me know in person if the game is horribly broken; I worked on it all week and didn't test it.
